<BODY     >

 <H1>Degrees of Dynamism</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Static
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>complete system behavior described at build time
<LI>examples: Wright, UniCON, etc.
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Closed dynamic
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>complete system behavior described at build time
<LI>describe changes during design (must predict change)
<LI>examples: DARWIN, Rapide
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Open dynamic
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>system behavior may evolve after build time
<LI>describe previously unanticipated changes during runtime
<LI>examples: C2</UL></UL></P>
<P></P> 
